{"tid":1027514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實，你最珍貴。","createTime":"2019-02-19T00:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T01:17:03.000Z","uid":9865,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a6ebc7c4eb56ebf4692e2e051250eac9db2e78","tid":1027514,"uid":9865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"我地成日羨慕人地，<br />\n覺得人地有幾好有幾叻，<br />\n然後忘記咗自己原來都唔差架喎。<br />\n我地知道別人嘅珍貴，<br />\n然後又忘記自己都係獨一無二，<br />\n你要記住你有D野係人地無架，<br />\n所以你最珍貴。<br />\n好多時候只係自己太想得到一個輸贏。<br />\n贏，唔一定要係兩性之間決定一個勝負，<br />\n只要你好好珍惜自己，珍惜身邊嘅每一個，<br />\n你已經係最大嘅贏家。"},{"pid":"effb9b07d9dcd7280c8d589c08e783f6c167b384","tid":1027514,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eed85b4e3319aed1f1835cde6ba19ea5c73b9c2","tid":1027514,"uid":9865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"effb9b07d9dcd7280c8d589c08e783f6c167b384","tid":1027514,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"記住 你最珍貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}